<eesti> Artikkel 9 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The residence documents granted to nationals of a Member State of the EEC referred to in this Directive shall be issued and renewed free of charge or on payment of an amount not exceeding the dues and taxes charged for the issue of identity cards to nationals. </inglise>
